    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts reliably, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and functionally sound. Potential buyers can expect a dependable driving experience with no immediate repairs needed.",
