    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that defies its age. This unit remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously preserved and mechanically absolute, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the collector who demands nothing less than perfection. It is an investment-grade acquisition for the most discerning automotive enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
